        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>heated basmati rice</strong> and <strong>veg\u00a0stock</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 1-2 min or until the prawns are cooked through \u2013 this is your\u00a0<strong>smoky Spanish king prawn rice</strong></p>",
